<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFE1FFD5F873598F5CCAFC11" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFE1FFD5F873598F52A7FD8B" blockId="12.[1995,2596,390,817]" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">
<emphasis id="B918CD75FFE1FFD5F873598F520BFE33" bold="true" box="[1999,2154,390,423]" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5F737598F52F7FE5B" authority="Moojen, 1948" authorityName="Moojen" authorityYear="1948" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Proechimys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="iheringi" subSpecies="gratiosus">Proechimys iheringi gratiosus Moojen, 1948</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="3B041B3AFFE1FFD5F71759BB52A7FD8B" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3804303367" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">“Floresta da Caixa Dagua, Santa Teresa, Espirito Santo, Brazil; altitude 750 meters.”</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFE1FFD5F8775A2D5CCAFC11" blockId="12.[1995,2596,390,817]" lastBlockId="12.[1386,2606,825,2791]" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">
J. Moojen described three taxa in 1948 as subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5F76B5A42527BFD07" authorityName="Moojen" authorityYear="1948" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Proechimys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="iheringi" subSpecies="gratiosus">Proechimys iheringi gratiosus</taxonomicName>
, bonafider, and panema. M. C. Lara and J. L. Patton in 2000; transferred all to 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5F8695AC85226FD76" authorityName=" Thomas" authorityYear="1921" box="[2005,2119,705,738]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Trinomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Trinomys</taxonomicName>
, elevated 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5F7615AC8532EFD76" authorityName="Moojen" authorityYear="1948" box="[2269,2383,705,738]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Trinomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gratiosus">gratiosus</taxonomicName>
to species status, and treated bonafidei as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5F86A5B19523BFCA5" baseAuthorityName="Thomas" baseAuthorityYear="1911" box="[2006,2138,784,817]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Proechimys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="iheringi">T. iheringi</taxonomicName>
. L.. M. Pessoa and colleagues in 2015 included panema as a junior synonym of the nominate subspecies 
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5F6D95B3053B9FCCE" authorityName="Moojen" authorityYear="1948" box="[2405,2520,825,858]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Trinomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gratiosus">gratiosus</taxonomicName>
. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFE1FFD5FAD35B8253CEFBD3" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" type="synonymic_list">
<caption id="DF1341EFFFE1FFD5FAD35B8253CEFBD3" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6623702" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6623702" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6623702/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" targetBox="[1386,1976,406,818]" targetPageId="12">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFE1FFD5FAD35B825C9EFC38" blockId="12.[1386,2606,825,2791]" box="[1391,1791,907,940]" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">
<emphasis id="B918CD75FFE1FFD5FAD35B825C9EFC38" bold="true" box="[1391,1791,907,940]" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">Subspecies and Distribution.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFE1FFD5FACF5BB95C49FBB7" blockId="12.[1386,2606,825,2791]" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5FACF5BB95C8EFC45" authority="Moojen, 1948" authorityName="Moojen" authorityYear="1948" baseAuthorityName="Moojen" baseAuthorityYear="1948" box="[1395,1775,944,977]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Trinomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="gratiosus" subSpecies="gratiosus">T.g.gratiosusMoojen,1948—SEBrazil,coastalEspiritoSantoandNERiodeJaneirostates,andinlandtoSMinasGeraisStateandItatiaiaNationalParkinNWRiodeJaneiroState.</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFE1FFD5FACF5C2F53CEFBD3" blockId="12.[1386,2606,825,2791]" box="[1395,2479,1062,1095]" pageId="12" pageNumber="564">
<taxonomicName id="4C6C6AE4FFE1FFD5FACF5C2F5C8FFBD3" authority="Moojen, 1948" authorityName="Moojen" authorityYear="1948" box="[1395,1774,1062,1095]" class="Mammalia" family="Echimyidae" genus="Trinomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="12" pageNumber="564" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="gratiosus" subSpecies="bonafidei">T. g. bonafidei Moojen, 1948</taxonomicName>
— SE Brazil, coastal ranges of Rio de Janeiro State.
</paragraph>
</caption>
